{"tid":1633853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［不割席］希望大家Be Water之餘記得Be Humble","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:59:49.000Z","uid":107099,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9d773662178e249f584c3ed120ae5f224e2ccf","tid":1633853,"uid":107099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次出post 因為真係有啲說話不吐不快<br />\n唔係割席 唔係分化 只係想提醒返各位手足<br />\n我地除左Be Water之外 都要Be Humble<br />\n好耐好耐之前 運動啱啱開始既時候<br />\n大家都進化都好快 改善得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為大家都好虛心咁去接受人地意見<br />\n以前大家見到人地影相好嬲會直接屌埋去<br />\n「屌你老母影乜撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n後尾有手足提醒要注意態度 唔使咁惡<br />\n進化成「唔好意思呀請你唔好影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n前線手足們 依家既連登個氣氛好奇怪<br />\n好似一檢討就會比人屌割席 前線決定呀之類<br />\n<strong>但真正既不割席係即使你做法唔完美都好 <br />\n我都會包容接納你 比空間你成長同改善</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而唔係睇住你一直咁犯同樣既錯誤</span><br />\n希望大家喺今後既日子入面聽到其他人既意見時<br />\n虛心冷靜落黎思考人地既講法有冇道理<br />\n<br />\n發夢既時候都要保持謙虛<br />\n例如rb 啲人想過 可以講<br />\n「唔好意思呀我地呢到封左<br />\n其實轉個彎仲有路行架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\nrather than 「屌你 你叫我比條路你行？<br />\n我都想叫林鄭比條路我行呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n咁樣對件事冇幫助之餘 又影響形象<br />\n<br />\n互勉<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a164f8f7266986a31772b4d23fa3baeecd953b1b","tid":1633853,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:30:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2329dab65fe0ff11593a00c1f80e1f9d8995c8b","tid":1633853,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:31:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83cd89d86c850863499ddd5f23658fff222f7f8e","tid":1633853,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"好有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908a87091dae13b203db394f050506012a7f5ca3","tid":1633853,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:32:34.000Z","msg":"發夢見到九龍城rb <br />\n對住前面個司機<br />\n個個淨係識講 「你問林鄭啦 我唔知」<br />\n根本唔識做好公關"},{"pid":"1f12d9202dceb8ffa62b51505cb4c455e266cc65","tid":1633853,"uid":187698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdf7b1fcf58988242712d44d09547ec9071336f4","tid":1633853,"uid":7231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:38:57.000Z","msg":"推 支持"},{"pid":"71e68cfbe64d19dfe16f6badab8eaae8b9399b46","tid":1633853,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"4dc8fbd2cdba003acadb3c6f2496515a1d41a6d3","tid":1633853,"uid":7231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03d33a184bc5b72e9780efa4c9cc9fbb93b31c22","tid":1633853,"uid":107099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:35.000Z","msg":"好似要自推十次 一"},{"pid":"12b00b49f81d22431beb80b1a7f014b5208d22df","tid":1633853,"uid":27821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8bd6294362cef4448700085a8eda6d929e67e9","tid":1633853,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"推 一樣諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者真係怒火無處發洩"},{"pid":"217f6dde2fb31d8e3ef00ab86824e5f2539ba127","tid":1633853,"uid":107099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201